{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<sub>","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>HTML <code>&lt;sub&gt;</code>&nbsp;元素</strong>定义了一个文本区域，出于排版的原因，与主要的文本相比，应该展示得更低并且更小。</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"en/HTML/Content categories\">内容分类</a></th>\n   <td>流式内容和短语内容</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">允许的内容</th>\n   <td>短语内容</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">标签省略</th>\n   <td>不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">允许的父元素</th>\n   <td>可以包含短语内容的任意元素</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">允许的&nbsp;ARIA 角色</th>\n   <td>任意 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM 接口</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>这个元素仅仅包含<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">全局属性</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法注解","title":"用法注解","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>这个元素应该只用于排版目的，也就是改变文本的位置会改变含义，例如在数学中（<var>t<sub>2</sub></var>，也可以考虑使用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML\" title=\"en/MathML\">MathML</a>&nbsp;公式）或者化学符号（&nbsp;<code>H<sub>2</sub>O</code>）。</li>\n <li>这个元素不能用于样式上的目的，比如产品名称 LaTeX 的样式，这时应该使用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"en/CSS\">CSS</a>样式：&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/vertical-align\"><code>vertical-align</code></a> 属性的&nbsp;<code>sub</code>&nbsp;值能实现相同效果。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>The chemical formula of water: H<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>sub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>sub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>O<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"结果\">结果</h4>\n\n<p>The chemical formula of water: H<sub>2</sub>O</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/semantics.html#the-sub-and-sup-elements\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;sub&gt; and &lt;sup&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/textlevel-semantics.html#the-sub-and-sup-elements\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;sub&gt; and &lt;sup&gt;;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a> HTML 元素会产生上标。要注意，你不能同时使用它们，你需要&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML\" title=\"en/MathML\">MathML</a>&nbsp;来同时产生化学符号旁边的下标和上标，代表它的序号和核子数。</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\" title=\"en/MathML/Element/msub\"><code>&lt;msub&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\" title=\"en/MathML/Element/msup\"><code>&lt;msup&gt;</code></a>, 和&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\" title=\"en/MathML/Element/msubsup\"><code>&lt;msubsup&gt;</code></a> MathML 元素。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"用法注解","id":"用法注解"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"HTML <sub> 元素定义了一个文本区域，出于排版的原因，与主要的文本相比，应该展示得更低并且更小。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<sub>: The Subscript element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"sub","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<sub> : l'élément de souscription","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<sub>: 下付き文字要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<sub>: 아래 첨자 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/sub","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/sub/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub","title":"<sub>"}],"pageTitle":"<sub> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}